EFS:- elastic file system
it is fully managed file storage services
provided by aws.amazon.com
it allows multiple ec2 instance to access the same file system simultaneously.
scalable data storage for amazon ec2 vms
provide servelss fully elastic storage you can share data without storage capacity.

USES OF EFS;- 
       1) web application hosting 
       2) content managment system
       3) big data & analytics
       4) container storage


FEATURES OF EFS:- 
       1) fully managed file system
       2) automatic scaling
       3) support linux based workloads
       4) secure data ecryption
